# =============================================================================
# The SEO Agent skill suite. Environment config.
#
# You do NOT need any of this to run the free skills. The free agents
# (site audit, keyword research, content writing, content review, backlink
# scouting, markdown export) run entirely inside your own Claude, with no key
# and no account.
#
# Set these only when you want to unlock the paid agents (real DataForSEO data,
# automatic daily writing, one-click publishing to your CMS, the backlink
# exchange network). Get your key by signing up at https://www.theseoagent.ai
# =============================================================================

# Your The SEO Agent API key. Sign up (free), then copy it from Settings.
# Unlocks the paid agents. Leave blank to stay on the free tier.
THESEOAGENT_API_KEY=

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Optional: your OWN Google Search Console credentials.
#
# If you set these, the keyword-research and site-audit skills will pull your
# real impressions, clicks, and average positions (your data, free, straight
# from Google). This uses YOUR Google Cloud OAuth app, not ours. Setup steps
# are in skills/keyword-research/SKILL.md and google-search-console/SETUP.md.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
GSC_CLIENT_ID=
GSC_CLIENT_SECRET=
GSC_REFRESH_TOKEN=
GSC_PROPERTY_URL=
